scamp
  -Python package for simple climate modeling. With a few lines of code it is possible 
   to do customized oceanic modeling withpout opening the source code. The backbone of 
   the package is defined in classes.py.
  
examples
  -Python scripts with basic examples of how to use scamp. 
  
ipython-notebook
  -Interactive examples executed in ipython notebook. This includes a basic introduction to the scamp package and advanced examples with data-examples.
